Future Capital’s Second-Quarter Loan Book Was 20 Billion Rupees

-- B y   M a l a v i k a   S h a r m a
-- 
2011-10-20T04:48:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-20/future-capital-s-second-quarter-loan-book-was-20-billion-rupees.html
Future Capital Holdings Ltd. (FCHL) ’s loan
book was close to 20 billion rupees in the three months ended
Sept. 30, Managing Director V. Vaidyanathan said in an interview
to Bloomberg-UTV.  Vaidyanathan said he expects the  Reserve Bank  of India to
raise interest rates by 25 basis points in its policy
announcement on Oct. 25.  To contact the reporter on this story:
